      "widgets_values": [
        "ℹ️ S-17 Tone Match LUT — auto-generate a portable .cube from a graded reference frame\n\nChain: LoadImage (reference frame) → N-17 Tone Match LUT(level=8, filename=\"match.cube\") → ShowText. N-17 grades an identity HALD by LAB histogram matching, then exports the result as an Adobe Cube 1.0 file that can be re-used with N-14 LUT Import or loaded in Resolve / Premiere / OBS / OCIO.\n\nThis is the fastest route from a single hero frame to a reusable look. Feed it a finished graded still, then apply the generated .cube to other shots downstream."
